{"tid":1289251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB 節目「有福同享」教新香港人攞褔利","createTime":"2019-07-06T04:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T22:55:40.000Z","uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"46b0fcdd5c481c577dfe93db5740e8b57e3aa7c1","tid":1289251,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/programmes/titanwashingmachineacecleanerpresentswelfareweekly/5d16a41ae60383a3621e52d4/%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%92%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Ftitanwashingmachineacecleanerpresentswelfareweekly%2F5d16a41ae60383a3621e52d4%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2592%25AD&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=2d12f4dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/programmes/titanwashingmachineacecleanerpresentswelfareweekly/5d16a41ae60383a3621e52d4/%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%92%AD</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人享有的福利，大家知道有多少嗎？只要達到某些<br />\n歲數，就可以享有不同福利，例如高齡津貼。經濟有困難人士可享有社會保障，例如簡稱綜援的綜合社會保障援助計劃。其實，香港人在很多範疇都可享福利，從住屋、醫療、教育、稅收等方面，都有種種福利保障。你到底享有甚麼福利？節目會為大家介紹香港人享有的福利，實行「有福同享」！"},{"pid":"500e8019ea5046895e5cd9fe105d825029a249b6","tid":1289251,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"招人參加區議會選舉 減少建制派自動當選（長文）2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277363</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7899d44588f061419e8b8584aa30bca3911716c9","tid":1289251,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvSJXSZ.png\" data-thumbn